This design embodies the textured and intricate charm of vintage denim. Both the fur trim and hood are detachable, catering to versatile and ever-changing fashion inspirations. The ribbed waistline and hem create a flattering silhouette, while asymmetrical rectangular pockets add a touch of individuality. The ruched sleeve design enhances the layered look, exuding bold and edgy vibes. Detachable fur-lined hood Vintage distressed effect Cotton-padded lining design

The detachable fur trim and hood provide versatile styling options, catering to diverse fashion inspirations. Ribbed waistline and hem details create a flattering silhouette, while irregular rectangular pockets add a touch of individuality.
